{"type":"message","id":"ec5714fe","parentId":"6413661c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:14:53.720Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d54203a1808e3b58aa92bb3daf0f6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# API 配置和温度显示问题修复报告\r\n\r\n## 修复概览\r\n**修复时间**: 2026年4月1日 19:08-19:13\r\n**修复状态**: ✅ 已完成核心修复\r\n\r\n## 修复详情\r\n\r\n### 1. ✅ 温度显示异常 (0.00007%) \r\n**问题根因**: APISettings.tsx 中的温度转换逻辑错误\r\n**修复内容**:\r\n- 修改 `loadConfig()` 函数：温度值在存储时为0-1的小数，显示时转换为0-100的整数\r\n- 修改温度显示标签：使用 `Math.round()` 确保正确显示百分比\r\n- 修复前：`0.7` 显示为 `0.00007%`\r\n- 修复后：`0.7` 正确显示为 `70%`\r\n\r\n**代码变更**:\r\n```typescript\r\n// 修复前\r\ntemperature: config.temperature\r\n\r\n// 修复后\r\ntemperature: config.temperature ? Math.round(config.temperature * 100) : 70\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 2. ✅ API 连接测试失败\r\n**问题根因**: `aiService.testConnection()` 函数存在问题\r\n**修复内容**:\r\n- 增强 `testConnection()` 函数：添加API Key存在性检查\r\n- 改进错误处理：提供更详细的错误信息\r\n- 修复多服务商支持：为每个服务商使用正确的模型标识\r\n\r\n**代码变更**:\r\n```typescript\r\n// 修复前：简单的连接测试\r\nconst result = await call('你好，请回复\"连接成功\"。', {\r\n  systemPrompt: '你是一个测试助手。',\r\n  model: 'deepseek/deepseek-chat',\r\n});\r\n\r\n// 修复后：增强的连接测试\r\n// 1. 检查API Key是否存在\r\nconst apiKey = await getApiKeySecurely(targetService);\r\nif (!apiKey && targetService !== 'ollama') {\r\n  console.error(`${targetService} API Key 未配置`);\r\n  return false;\r\n}\r\n// 2. 使用正确的模型标识\r\n// 3. 改进错误处理\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 3. ✅ AI 工具提示未配置 API\r\n**问题根因**: `aiService.isConfiguredAsync()` 检查错误的服务商\r\n**修复内容**:\r\n- 修改 `isConfiguredAsync()` 函数：支持指定服务商检查\r\n- 改进默认检查逻辑：检查所有已知服务商是否有至少一个配置了API Key\r\n- 修复同步版本 `isConfigured()` 函数\r\n\r\n**代码变更**:\r\n```typescript\r\n// 修复前：只检查默认服务\r\nconst apiKey = await getApiKeySecurely('default');\r\n\r\n// 修复后：支持指定服务商或检查所有服务商\r\nif (service) {\r\n  const apiKey = await getApiKeySecurely(service);\r\n  return !!apiKey;\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 如果没有指定服务，检查所有已知服务商\r\nconst services = ['doubao', 'deepseek', 'kimi', 'openai'];\r\nfor (const svc of services) {\r\n  const apiKey = await getApiKeySecurely(svc);\r\n  if (apiKey) return true;\r\n}\r\nreturn false;\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 4. ✅ 默认模型选择问题\r\n**问题根因**: 高级设置中的下拉框没有默认选中值\r\n**修复内容**:\r\n- 修改 `loadConfig()` 函数：使用 `aiService.getDefaultModel()` 获取默认模型\r\n- 修改 `handleSave()` 函数：保存配置时同时保存默认模型\r\n- 确保下拉框有正确的选中值\r\n\r\n**代码变更**:\r\n```typescript\r\n// 修复前\r\nmodel: config.model,\r\n\r\n// 修复后\r\nmodel: aiService.getDefaultModel(),\r\n\r\n// 保存时额外保存默认模型\r\nif (values.model) {\r\n  aiService.setDefaultModel(values.model)\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 已验证的修复效果\r\n\r\n### ✅ 温度显示修复验证\r\n- 温度滑动条现在正确显示百分比（0-100）\r\n- 保存和加载配置时温度值正确转换\r\n- 显示格式：`温度 (70%）` 而不是 `温度 (0.00007%）`\r\n\r\n### ✅ API 连接测试修复验证\r\n- 各服务商API连接测试现在能正确检查API Key存在性\r\n- 测试失败时提供明确的错误信息\r\n- 支持多服务商独立测试\r\n\r\n### ✅ AI 工具提示修复验证\r\n- AI工具面板现在能正确检查API配置状态\r\n- 根据当前功能对应的服务商检查API Key\r\n- 提供更友好的错误提示\r\n\r\n### ✅ 默认模型选择修复验证\r\n- 高级设置中的默认模型下拉框现在有正确的选中值\r\n- 保存配置时同时保存默认模型设置\r\n- 加载配置时正确显示已保存的默认模型\r\n\r\n## 待优化的用户体验\r\n\r\n### 🔄 5. 优化用户体验和错误提示（建议）\r\n1. **API Key 配置状态可视化**\r\n   - 在AI工具面板显示当前有效的API配置\r\n   - 添加配置状态指示器（已配置/未配置）\r\n\r\n2. **更明确的错误引导**\r\n   - 当API Key未配置时，提供直接跳转到设置页面的链接\r\n   - 显示需要配置的具体服务商名称\r\n\r\n3. **成本预估优化**\r\n   - 在API设置页面显示更准确的成本预估\r\n   - 添加使用量统计和成本预测\r\n\r\n### 🔄 6. 测试所有修复（建议测试步骤）\r\n1. **温度设置测试**\r\n   - 设置不同温度值（0, 50, 100）\r\n   - 保存并重新加载页面验证持久化\r\n\r\n2. **API连接测试**\r\n   - 配置不同服务商的API Key\r\n   - 测试每个服务商的连接状态\r\n\r\n3. **AI工具功能测试**\r\n   - 在AI工具面板尝试生成功能\r\n   - 验证API检查逻辑的正确性\r\n\r\n4. **模型映射测试**\r\n   - 切换不同预设方案\r\n   - 验证功能-模型映射是否正确应用\r\n\r\n## 技术细节\r\n\r\n### 修复的文件\r\n1. `novel-desktop-app/src/renderer/src/components/APISettings.tsx`\r\n   - 温度显示和转换逻辑\r\n   - 默认模型加载和保存\r\n   - API连接测试界面\r\n\r\n2. `novel-desktop-app/src/renderer/src/services/aiService.ts`\r\n   - API连接测试函数\r\n   - API配置检查函数\r\n   - 模型映射管理\r\n\r\n### 核心修复原则\r\n1. **向后兼容**: 所有修复保持与现有代码的兼容性\r\n2. **用户友好**: 错误信息和界面提示更清晰\r\n3. **模块化**: 每个功能独立，便于维护和测试\r\n4. **安全性**: API Key 使用安全存储（加密存储）\r\n\r\n## 后续建议\r\n\r\n### 短期优化（1-2天）\r\n1. 添加API配置状态面板\r\n2. 优化错误提示和用户引导\r\n3. 添加使用量统计功能\r\n\r\n### 中期改进（1-2周）\r\n1. 实现更精确的成本计算\r\n2. 添加API使用监控和告警\r\n3. 优化多模型路由策略\r\n\r\n### 长期规划（1个月以上）\r\n1. 实现自动模型选择优化\r\n2. 添加批处理和多任务支持\r\n3. 集成更多AI服务商\r\n\r\n## 总结\r\n\r\n所有核心的API配置和温度显示问题已成功修复。主要成就：\r\n\r\n1. **温度显示**: 正确显示百分比，解决0.00007%异常\r\n2. **API连接**: 支持多服务商独立测试，提供明确错误信息\r\n3. **API检查**: 根据功能对应的服务商检查配置状态\r\n4. **模型选择**: 确保默认模型正确保存和加载\r\n\r\n系统现在提供更稳定和用户友好的AI服务配置体验。建议用户进行实际测试以验证修复效果，并根据使用反馈进行进一步的优化。\r\n\r\n---\r\n**修复完成时间**: 2026-04-01 19:13\r\n**修复人员**: Cline (AI助手)\r\n**验证状态**: ✅ 代码修复完成，建议进行功能测试\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775232893717}}
{"type":"message","id":"c6fd1354","parentId":"ec5714fe","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:14:55.901Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在让我查看更核心的代码文件来找出更多 bug。让我查看 aiService.ts 和 main.ts 中的潜在问题。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n让我继续审查核心文件：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_792535cf0fd7491187475d86","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/mnt/d/axs/novel-desktop-app/src/main/aiService.ts"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":29678,"output":71,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29749,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775232893720,"responseId":"chatcmpl-332508d7-8df7-4415-ad44-d320088fa932"}}
{"type":"message","id":"28b6728a","parentId":"c6fd1354","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:14:55.924Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_792535cf0fd7491187475d86","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// 主进程 AI 服务 - 安全的 API 调用实现\r\n// 所有 AI 调用都在主进程执行，避免 API Key 暴露在渲染进程\r\n\r\nimport { safeStorage } from 'electron'\r\nimport type { IpcMainInvokeEvent } from 'electron'\r\n\r\n// 延迟初始化 store\r\nlet store: any = null\r\n\r\nasync function getStore() {\r\n  if (!store) {\r\n    const Store = (await import('electron-store')).default\r\n    store = new Store({\r\n      name: 'ai-config',\r\n      encryptionKey: 'novel-ai-writing-assistant-2024',\r\n    })\r\n  }\r\n  return store\r\n}\r\n\r\n// API Key 缓存\r\nconst apiKeyCache: Map<string, string> = new Map()\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 加密并存储 API Key\r\n */\r\nexport async function saveApiKey(service: string, apiKey: string): Promise<void> {\r\n  const storeInstance = await getStore()\r\n  try {\r\n    const encrypted = safeStorage.encryptString(apiKey)\r\n    storeInstance.set(`api_key_${service}`, encrypted)\r\n    apiKeyCache.set(service, apiKey)\r\n  } catch (error) {\r\n    console.error(`加密 ${service} API Key 失败:`, error)\r\n    // 降级：明文存储（不推荐）\r\n    storeInstance.set(`api_key_${service}_plain`, apiKey)\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 获取 API Key\r\n */\r\nexport async function getApiKey(service: string): Promise<string | null> {\r\n  // 检查缓存\r\n  if (apiKeyCache.has(service)) {\r\n    return apiKeyCache.get(service)!\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  const storeInstance = await getStore()\r\n  try {\r\n    // 尝试解密\r\n    const encrypted = storeInstance.get(`api_key_${service}`) as Buffer | undefined\r\n    if (encrypted) {\r\n      const decrypted = safeStorage.decryptString(encrypted)\r\n      apiKeyCache.set(service, decrypted)\r\n      return decrypted\r\n    }\r\n  } catch (error) {\r\n    console.error(`解密 ${service} API Key 失败:`, error)\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  // 降级：尝试获取明文\r\n  const plainKey = storeInstance.get(`api_key_${service}_plain`) as string | undefined\r\n  if (plainKey) {\r\n    apiKeyCache.set(service, plainKey)\r\n    return plainKey\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  return null\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 检查服务是否已配置\r\n */\r\nexport async function isServiceConfigured(service: string): Promise<boolean> {\r\n  const key = await getApiKey(service)\r\n  return !!key\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 获取所有已配置的服务列表\r\n */\r\nexport async function getConfiguredServices(): Promise<string[]> {\r\n  const services = ['doubao', 'deepseek', 'kimi', 'openai', 'ollama']\r\n  const configured: string[] = []\r\n  \r\n  for (const service of services) {\r\n    if (await isServiceConfigured(service)) {\r\n      configured.push(service)\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  return configured\r\n}\r\n\r\n// ==================== 豆包接入点 ID 映射 ====================\r\n\r\n// 豆包 API 要求使用 ep- 开头的接入点 ID，不能使用模型名\r\n// 模型名仅用于创建接入点，调用时必须用 ep- 开头的接入点 ID\r\nconst DOUBAO_ENDPOINT_MAP: Record<string, string> = {\r\n  // pro 系列\r\n  'doubao-seed-2.0-pro-32k': 'ep-20260401204837-jklzh',\r\n  'doubao-seed-2.0-pro-256k': 'ep-20260401204837-jklzh',\r\n  'doubao-1-5-ultra-256k': 'ep-20260401204837-jklzh',\r\n  'doubao-pro': 'ep-20260401204837-jklzh',\r\n  // lite 系列\r\n  'doubao-seed-2.0-lite-32k': 'ep-20260401210511-qhg9m',\r\n  'doubao-seed-2.0-lite-256k': 'ep-20260401210511-qhg9m',\r\n  'doubao-lite': 'ep-20260401210511-qhg9m',\r\n  // mini 系列\r\n  'doubao-seed-2.0-mini-32k': 'ep-20260401205747-4csq4',\r\n  'doubao-seed-2.0-mini-256k': 'ep-20260401205747-4csq4',\r\n  'doubao-mini': 'ep-20260401205747-4csq4',\r\n};\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 将豆包模型名解析为接入点 ID\r\n * 如果已经是 ep- 开头，直接返回\r\n * 如果匹配不到，抛出明确错误\r\n */\r\nfunction resolveDoubaoModelId(modelName: string): string {\r\n  // 已经是接入点 ID，直接返回\r\n  if (modelName.startsWith('ep-')) {\r\n    return modelName;\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  // 精确匹配\r\n  const lower = modelName.toLowerCase();\r\n  if (DOUBAO_ENDPOINT_MAP[lower]) {\r\n    return DOUBAO_ENDPOINT_MAP[lower];\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  // 关键词匹配\r\n  if (lower.includes('pro')) {\r\n    return DOUBAO_ENDPOINT_MAP['doubao-pro'];\r\n  } else if (lower.includes('lite')) {\r\n    return DOUBAO_ENDPOINT_MAP['doubao-lite'];\r\n  } else if (lower.includes('mini')) {\r\n    return DOUBAO_ENDPOINT_MAP['doubao-mini'];\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  // 无法识别的豆包模型\r\n  throw new Error(`不支持豆包模型 ${modelName}，请使用 pro/lite/mini 类型的豆包模型`);\r\n}\r\n\r\n// ==================== 模型调用实现 ====================\r\n\r\nexport interface AICallOptions {\r\n  function?: string\r\n  model?: string\r\n  temperature?: number\r\n  maxTokens?: number\r\n  systemPrompt?: string\r\n  stream?: boolean\r\n  reasoningEffort?: 'low' | 'medium' | 'high'\r\n}\r\n\r\nexport interface StreamChunk {\r\n  content: string\r\n  done: boolean\r\n  reasoning?: string // DeepSeek-R1 专用\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 豆包 API 调用\r\n */\r\nexport async function callDoubao(prompt: string, options: AICallOptions & { model: string }): Promise<string> {\r\n  const apiKey = await getApiKey('doubao')\r\n  if (!apiKey) throw new Error('未配置豆包 API Key')\r\n\r\n  // 将模型名解析为接入点 ID（豆包 API 要求使用 ep- 开头的 ID）\r\n  const endpointId = resolveDoubaoModelId(options.model)\r\n\r\n  const response = await fetch('https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/chat/completions', {\r\n    method: 'POST',\r\n    headers: {\r\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\r\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${apiKey}`,\r\n    },\r\n    body: JSON.stringify({\r\n      model: endpointId,\r\n      messages: [{ role: 'user', content: prompt }],\r\n      temperature: options.temperature ?? 0.7,\r\n      max_tokens: options.maxTokens ?? 2000,\r\n      top_p: 0.95,\r\n    }),\r\n  })\r\n\r\n  const data: any = await response.json()\r\n  if (!response.ok) throw new Error(data.error?.message || '豆包调用失败')\r\n  return data.choices[0].message.content\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 豆包流式调用\r\n */\r\nexport async function* streamDoubao(prompt: string, options: AICallOptions & { model: string }): AsyncGenerator<StreamChunk> {\r\n  const apiKey = await getApiKey('doubao')\r\n  if (!apiKey) throw new Error('未配置豆包 API Key')\r\n\r\n  // 将模型名解析为接入点 ID（豆包 API 要求使用 ep- 开头的 ID）\r\n  const endpointId = resolveDoubaoModelId(options.model)\r\n\r\n  const response = await fetch('https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/chat/completions', {\r\n    method: 'POST',\r\n    headers: {\r\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\r\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${apiKey}`,\r\n    },\r\n    body: JSON.stringify({\r\n      model: endpointId,\r\n      messages: [{ role: 'user', content: prompt }],\r\n      temperature: options.temperature ?? 0.7,\r\n      max_tokens: options.maxTokens ?? 2000,\r\n      top_p: 0.95,\r\n      stream: true,\r\n    }),\r\n  })\r\n\r\n  if (!response.ok) {\r\n    const error = await response.text()\r\n    throw new Error(`豆包调用失败：${response.status} - ${error}`)\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  const reader = response.body?.getReader()\r\n  if (!reader) throw new Error('无法读取响应流')\r\n\r\n  const decoder = new TextDecoder('utf-8')\r\n  let buffer = ''\r\n\r\n  while (true) {\r\n    const { done, value } = await reader.read()\r\n    if (done) break\r\n\r\n    buffer += decoder.decode(value, { stream: true })\r\n    const lines = buffer.split('\\n')\r\n    buffer = lines.pop() || ''\r\n\r\n    for (const line of lines) {\r\n      const trimmed = line.trim()\r\n      if (trimmed.startsWith('data: ')) {\r\n        const data = trimmed.slice(6)\r\n        if (data === '[DONE]') {\r\n          yield { content: '', done: true }\r\n          return\r\n        }\r\n        try {\r\n          const parsed: any = JSON.parse(data)\r\n          const content = parsed.choices?.[0]?.delta?.content || ''\r\n          if (content) yield { content, done: false }\r\n        } catch (e) {\r\n          console.warn('解析流数据失败:', e)\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * DeepSeek API 调用\r\n */\r\nexport async function callDeepSeek(prompt: string, options: AICallOptions & { model: string }): Promise<string> {\r\n  const apiKey = await getApiKey('deepseek')\r\n  if (!apiKey) throw new Error('未配置 DeepSeek API Key')\r\n\r\n  const isReasoner = options.model === 'deepseek-reasoner'\r\n  const body: any = {\r\n    model: options.model,\r\n    messages: [{ role: 'user', content: prompt }],\r\n    temperature: options.temperature ?? 0.7,\r\n    max_tokens: options.maxTokens ?? 2000,\r\n  }\r\n  if (isReasoner && options.reasoningEffort) {\r\n    body.reasoning_effort = options.reasoningEffort\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  const response = await fetch('https://api.deepseek.com/v1/chat/completions', {\r\n    method: 'POST',\r\n    headers: {\r\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\r\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${apiKey}`,\r\n    },\r\n    body: JSON.stringify(body),\r\n  })\r\n\r\n  const data: any = await response.json()\r\n  if (!response.ok) throw new Error(data.error?.message || 'DeepSeek 调用失败')\r\n  return data.choices[0].message.content\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * DeepSeek 流式调用\r\n */\r\nexport async function* streamDeepSeek(prompt: string, options: AICallOptions & { model: string }): AsyncGenerator<StreamChunk> {\r\n  const apiKey = await getApiKey('deepseek')\r\n  if (!apiKey) throw new Error('未配置 DeepSeek API Key')\r\n\r\n  const isReasoner = options.model === 'deepseek-reasoner'\r\n  const body: any = {\r\n    model: options.model,\r\n    messages: [{ role: 'user', content: prompt }],\r\n    temperature: options.temperature ?? 0.7,\r\n    max_tokens: options.maxTokens ?? 2000,\r\n    stream: true,\r\n  }\r\n  if (isReasoner && options.reasoningEffort) {\r\n    body.reasoning_effort = options.reasoningEffort\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  const response = await fetch('https://api.deepseek.com/v1/chat/completions', {\r\n    method: 'POST',\r\n    headers: {\r\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\r\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${apiKey}`,\r\n    },\r\n    body: JSON.stringify(body),\r\n  })\r\n\r\n  if (!response.ok) {\r\n    const error = await response.text()\r\n    throw new Error(`DeepSeek 调用失败：${response.status} - ${error}`)\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  const reader = response.body?.getReader()\r\n  if (!reader) throw new Error('无法读取响应流')\r\n\r\n  const decoder = new TextDecoder('utf-8')\r\n  let buffer = ''\r\n\r\n  while (true) {\r\n    const { done, value } = await reader.read()\r\n    if (done) break\r\n\r\n    buffer += decoder.decode(value, { stream: true })\r\n    const lines = buffer.split('\\n')\r\n    buffer = lines.pop() || ''\r\n\r\n    for (const line of lines) {\r\n      const trimmed = line.trim()\r\n      if (trimmed.startsWith('data: ')) {\r\n        const data = trimmed.slice(6)\r\n        if (data === '[DONE]') {\r\n          yield { content: '', done: true }\r\n          return\r\n        }\r\n        try {\r\n          const parsed: any = JSON.parse(data)\r\n          const content = parsed.choices?.[0]?.delta?.content || ''\r\n          const reasoning = parsed.choices?.[0]?.delta?.reasoning_content || ''\r\n          if (content || reasoning) {\r\n            yield { content, done: false, reasoning }\r\n          }\r\n        } catch (e) {\r\n          console.warn('解析流数据失败:', e)\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * Kimi API 调用\r\n */\r\nexport async function callKimi(prompt: string, options: AICallOptions & { model: string }): Promise<string> {\r\n  const apiKey = await getApiKey('kimi')\r\n  if (!apiKey) throw new Error('未配置 Kimi API Key')\r\n\r\n  const response = await fetch('https://api.moonshot.cn/v1/chat/completions', {\r\n    method: 'POST',\r\n    headers: {\r\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\r\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${apiKey}`,\r\n    },\r\n    body: JSON.stringify({\r\n      model: options.model,\r\n      messages: [{ role: 'user', content: prompt }],\r\n      temperature: options.temperature ?? 0.7,\r\n      max_tokens: options.maxTokens ?? 2000,\r\n    }),\r\n  })\r\n\r\n  const data: any = await response.json()\r\n  if (!response.ok) throw new Error(data.error?.message || 'Kimi 调用失败')\r\n  return data.choices[0].message.content\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * Kimi 流式调用\r\n */\r\nexport async function* streamKimi(prompt: string, options: AICallOptions & { model: string }): AsyncGenerator<StreamChunk> {\r\n  const apiKey = await getApiKey('kimi')\r\n  if (!apiKey) throw new Error('未配置 Kimi API Key')\r\n\r\n  const response = await fetch('https://api.moonshot.cn/v1/chat/completions', {\r\n    method: 'POST',\r\n    headers: {\r\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\r\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${apiKey}`,\r\n    },\r\n    body: JSON.stringify({\r\n      model: options.model,\r\n      messages: [{ role: 'user', content: prompt }],\r\n      temperature: options.temperature ?? 0.7,\r\n      max_tokens: options.maxTokens ?? 2000,\r\n      stream: true,\r\n    }),\r\n  })\r\n\r\n  if (!response.ok) {\r\n    const error = await response.text()\r\n    throw new Error(`Kimi 调用失败：${response.status} - ${error}`)\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  const reader = response.body?.getReader()\r\n  if (!reader) throw new Error('无法读取响应流')\r\n\r\n  const decoder = new TextDecoder('utf-8')\r\n  let buffer = ''\r\n\r\n  while (true) {\r\n    const { done, value } = await reader.read()\r\n    if (done) break\r\n\r\n    buffer += decoder.decode(value, { stream: true })\r\n    const lines = buffer.split('\\n')\r\n    buffer = lines.pop() || ''\r\n\r\n    for (const line of lines) {\r\n      const trimmed = line.trim()\r\n      if (trimmed.startsWith('data: ')) {\r\n        const data = trimmed.slice(6)\r\n        if (data === '[DONE]') {\r\n          yield { content: '', done: true }\r\n          return\r\n        }\r\n        try {\r\n          const parsed: any = JSON.parse(data)\r\n          const content = parsed.choices?.[0]?.delta?.content || ''\r\n          if (content) yield { content, done: false }\r\n        } catch (e) {\r\n          console.warn('解析流数据失败:', e)\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * OpenAI API 调用\r\n */\r\nexport async function callOpenAI(prompt: string, options: AICallOptions & { model: string }): Promise<string> {\r\n  const apiKey = await getApiKey('openai')\r\n  if (!apiKey) throw new Error('未配置 OpenAI API Key')\r\n\r\n  const storeInstance = await getStore()\r\n  const baseURL = storeInstance.get('openai_base_url', 'https://api.openai.com/v1') as string\r\n  const response = await fetch(`${baseURL}/chat/completions`, {\r\n    method: 'POST',\r\n    headers: {\r\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\r\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${apiKey}`,\r\n    },\r\n    body: JSON.stringify({\r\n      model: options.model,\r\n      messages: [{ role: 'user', content: prompt }],\r\n      temperature: options.temperature ?? 0.7,\r\n      max_tokens: options.maxTokens ?? 2000,\r\n    }),\r\n  })\r\n\r\n  const data: any = await response.json()\r\n  if (!response.ok) throw new Error(data.error?.message || 'OpenAI 调用失败')\r\n  return data.choices[0].message.content\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * OpenAI 流式调用\r\n */\r\nexport async function* streamOpenAI(prompt: string, options: AICallOptions & { model: string }): AsyncGenerator<StreamChunk> {\r\n  const apiKey = await getApiKey('openai')\r\n  if (!apiKey) throw new Error('未配置 OpenAI API Key')\r\n\r\n  const storeInstance = await getStore()\r\n  const baseURL = storeInstance.get('openai_base_url', 'https://api.openai.com/v1') as string\r\n  const response = await fetch(`${baseURL}/chat/completions`, {\r\n    method: 'POST',\r\n    headers: {\r\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\r\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${apiKey}`,\r\n    },\r\n    body: JSON.stringify({\r\n      model: options.model,\r\n      messages: [{ role: 'user', content: prompt }],\r\n      temperature: options.temperature ?? 0.7,\r\n      max_tokens: options.maxTokens ?? 2000,\r\n      stream: true,\r\n    }),\r\n  })\r\n\r\n  if (!response.ok) {\r\n    const error = await response.text()\r\n    throw new Error(`OpenAI 调用失败：${response.status} - ${error}`)\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  const reader = response.body?.getReader()\r\n  if (!reader) throw new Error('无法读取响应流')\r\n\r\n  const decoder = new TextDecoder('utf-8')\r\n  let buffer = ''\r\n\r\n  while (true) {\r\n    const { done, value } = await reader.read()\r\n    if (done) break\r\n\r\n    buffer += decoder.decode(value, { stream: true })\r\n    const lines = buffer.split('\\n')\r\n    buffer = lines.pop() || ''\r\n\r\n    for (const line of lines) {\r\n      const trimmed = line.trim()\r\n      if (trimmed.startsWith('data: ')) {\r\n        const data = trimmed.slice(6)\r\n        if (data === '[DONE]') {\r\n          yield { content: '', done: true }\r\n          return\r\n        }\r\n        try {\r\n          const parsed: any = JSON.parse(data)\r\n          const content = parsed.choices?.[0]?.delta?.content || ''\r\n          if (content) yield { content, done: false }\r\n        } catch (e) {\r\n          console.warn('解析流数据失败:', e)\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * Ollama 本地模型调用\r\n */\r\nexport async function callOllama(prompt: string, options: AICallOptions & { model: string }): Promise<string> {\r\n  const storeInstance = await getStore()\r\n  const url = storeInstance.get('ollama_url', 'http://localhost:11434') as string\r\n  const response = await fetch(`${url}/api/generate`, {\r\n    method: 'POST',\r\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\r\n    body: JSON.stringify({\r\n      model: options.model,\r\n      prompt,\r\n      stream: false,\r\n      options: {\r\n        temperature: options.temperature ?? 0.7,\r\n        num_predict: options.maxTokens ?? 2000,\r\n      },\r\n    }),\r\n  })\r\n\r\n  const data: any = await response.json()\r\n  return data.response\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * Ollama 流式调用\r\n */\r\nexport async function* streamOllama(prompt: string, options: AICallOptions & { model: string }): AsyncGenerator<StreamChunk> {\r\n  const storeInstance = await getStore()\r\n  const url = storeInstance.get('ollama_url', 'http://localhost:11434') as string\r\n  const response = await fetch(`${url}/api/generate`, {\r\n    method: 'POST',\r\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\r\n    body: JSON.stringify({\r\n      model: options.model,\r\n      prompt,\r\n      stream: true,\r\n      options: {\r\n        temperature: options.temperature ?? 0.7,\r\n        num_predict: options.maxTokens ?? 2000,\r\n      },\r\n    }),\r\n  })\r\n\r\n  if (!response.ok) {\r\n    const error = await response.text()\r\n    throw new Error(`Ollama 调用失败：${response.status} - ${error}`)\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  const reader = response.body?.getReader()\r\n  if (!reader) throw new Error('无法读取响应流')\r\n\r\n  const decoder = new TextDecoder('utf-8')\r\n  let buffer = ''\r\n\r\n  while (true) {\r\n    const { done, value } = await reader.read()\r\n    if (done) break\r\n\r\n    buffer += decoder.decode(value, { stream: true })\r\n    const lines = buffer.split('\\n')\r\n    buffer = lines.pop() || ''\r\n\r\n    for (const line of lines) {\r\n      if (!line.trim()) continue\r\n      try {\r\n        const parsed: any = JSON.parse(line)\r\n        const content = parsed.response || ''\r\n        if (content) yield { content, done: false }\r\n        if (parsed.done) {\r\n          yield { content: '', done: true }\r\n          return\r\n        }\r\n      } catch (e) {\r\n        console.warn('解析 Ollama 流数据失败:', e)\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// ==================== 模型路由 ====================\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 解析模型标识\r\n */\r\nfunction parseModelIdentifier(model: string): { service: string; modelName: string } {\r\n  const parts = model.split('/')\r\n  if (parts.length >= 2) {\r\n    return {\r\n      service: parts[0],\r\n      modelName: parts.slice(1).join('/'),\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  // 兼容旧格式\r\n  if (model.includes('doubao')) return { service: 'doubao', modelName: model }\r\n  if (model.includes('kimi') || model.includes('moonshot')) return { service: 'kimi', modelName: model }\r\n  if (model.includes('deepseek')) return { service: 'deepseek', modelName: model }\r\n  if (model.includes('gpt') || model.includes('openai')) return { service: 'openai', modelName: model }\r\n  if (model.includes('ollama') || model.includes('qwen') || model.includes('llama')) return { service: 'ollama', modelName: model }\r\n  return { service: 'deepseek', modelName: model }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 主调用函数（非流式）\r\n */\r\nexport async function callAI(prompt: string, options: AICallOptions = {}): Promise<string> {\r\n  const { model: directModel } = options\r\n  if (!directModel) throw new Error('必须指定模型')\r\n\r\n  const { service, modelName } = parseModelIdentifier(directModel)\r\n\r\n  switch (service) {\r\n    case 'doubao':\r\n      return callDoubao(prompt, { ...options, model: modelName })\r\n    case 'deepseek':\r\n      return callDeepSeek(prompt, { ...options, model: modelName })\r\n    case 'kimi':\r\n      return callKimi(prompt, { ...options, model: modelName })\r\n    case 'openai':\r\n      return callOpenAI(prompt, { ...options, model: modelName })\r\n    case 'ollama':\r\n      return callOllama(prompt, { ...options, model: modelName })\r\n    default:\r\n      throw new Error(`未知服务：${service}`)\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 主调用函数（流式）\r\n */\r\nexport async function* streamAI(prompt: string, options: AICallOptions = {}): AsyncGenerator<StreamChunk> {\r\n  const { model: directModel } = options\r\n  if (!directModel) throw new Error('必须指定模型')\r\n\r\n  const { service, modelName } = parseModelIdentifier(directModel)\r\n\r\n  switch (service) {\r\n    case 'doubao':\r\n      yield* streamDoubao(prompt, { ...options, model: modelName })\r\n      break\r\n    case 'deepseek':\r\n      yield* streamDeepSeek(prompt, { ...options, model: modelName })\r\n      break\r\n    case 'kimi':\r\n      yield* streamKimi(prompt, { ...options, model: modelName })\r\n      break\r\n    case 'openai':\r\n      yield* streamOpenAI(prompt, { ...options, model: modelName })\r\n      break\r\n    case 'ollama':\r\n      yield* streamOllama(prompt, { ...options, model: modelName })\r\n      break\r\n    default:\r\n      throw new Error(`未知服务：${service}`)\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 测试连接\r\n */\r\nexport async function testConnection(service: string): Promise<boolean> {\r\n  try {\r\n    const testPrompt = '你好，请回复\"连接成功\"。'\r\n    const testModel = service === 'doubao' ? 'doubao/doubao-seed-2.0-pro-32k'\r\n      : service === 'deepseek' ? 'deepseek/deepseek-chat'\r\n      : service === 'kimi' ? 'kimi/moonshot-v1-128k'\r\n      : service === 'openai' ? 'openai/gpt-4o-mini'\r\n      : 'ollama/qwen2.5:7b-q4_K_M'\r\n\r\n    const result = await callAI(testPrompt, { model: testModel })\r\n    return result.includes('连接成功') || result.length > 0\r\n  } catch (error) {\r\n    console.error(`${service} 连接测试失败:`, error)\r\n    return false\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775232895922}}
