{"type":"message","id":"02941916","parentId":"5cab043d","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:22:30.391Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Claude Code 已经安装了！用户问能不能调用 Claude Code，答案是能的。\n\n我可以调用 Claude Code 来帮助用户完成编码任务。根据技能文档，我需要使用：\n- `claude --permission-mode bypassPermissions --print 'task'`\n\n让我告诉用户可以调用，并询问他们想做什么任务。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n可以！Claude Code 已安装 (版本 2.1.87)。\n\n你想让 Claude Code 帮你做什么？比如：\n- 写代码 / 创建新功能\n- 代码审查 / 重构\n- 修复 Bug\n- 其他Coding任务"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":34634,"output":111,"cacheRead":14208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48953,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775233340900,"responseId":"019d5426647e48411076c6241cb9f8df"}}
